      <div class="services container" id="services">
        <h2 class="w3-center">Our services</h2>
        <div class="cards w3-padding-large w3-margin-top">
          <div class="card w3-card-2 w3-padding-large w3-border w3-border-blue w3-round-large">
            <h3>Blood donation: A lifeline for humanity's safety and survival.</h3>
            <div class="card-text">
              <p>Personal Health Benefits: Blood donation not only benefits recipients but also offers advantages to donors themselves. Donating blood can stimulate the production of new blood cells in the body, promoting cardiovascular health and reducing the risk of certain diseases such as heart disease and cancer. Additionally, blood donation provides an opportunity for individuals to undergo health screening tests, including blood pressure, hemoglobin levels, and infectious disease screening, offering insights into their overall health status.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="card w3-card-2 w3-padding-large w3-border w3-border-blue w3-round-large">
            <h3>"Blood donation: Saving lives, safeguarding humanity."</h3>
            <div class="card-text">
              <p> Lifesaving Impact: Blood donation plays a crucial role in saving lives, especially in emergencies, surgeries, and medical treatments for various illnesses. Donated blood provides essential support to patients suffering from conditions such as cancer, anemia, and blood disorders, contributing directly to their recovery and survival..</p>
            </div>
